    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>最近有人问起hexo博客，一直都有听说，却没有尝试过，先简单的看一下主题相关内容。<br>hexo 官方地址：<a href="https://hexo.io/">https://hexo.io/</a></p><p><img src="/2022/07/20/Butterfly/1.png" alt="butterfly"></p><h2 id="1、配置文件介绍"><a href="#1、配置文件介绍" class="headerlink" title="1、配置文件介绍"></a>1、配置文件介绍</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">SHELL</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost my_blog]# pwd</span><br><span class="line">/root/hexo/my_blog</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost my_blog]# ls</span><br><span class="line">_config.butterfly.yml  db.json       package-lock.json  source</span><br><span class="line">_config.landscape.yml  node_modules  public             themes</span><br><span class="line">_config.yml            package.json  scaffolds</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost my_blog]# </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（1）-config-yml-可以认为是全局配置文件，博客名称、语言、时间等"><a href="#（1）-config-yml-可以认为是全局配置文件，博客名称、语言、时间等" class="headerlink" title="（1）_config.yml 可以认为是全局配置文件，博客名称、语言、时间等"></a>（1）_config.yml 可以认为是全局配置文件，博客名称、语言、时间等</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">SHELL</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_"># </span><span class="language-bash">Site</span></span><br><span class="line">title: Happy Dog</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">description: &#x27;&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">keywords:</span><br><span class="line">author: Dog Y</span><br><span class="line">language: zh-CN</span><br><span class="line">timezone: &#x27;Asia/Shanghai&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="（2）-config-XXX-yml-主题相关配置文件"><a href="#（2）-config-XXX-yml-主题相关配置文件" class="headerlink" title="（2）_config.XXX.yml 主题相关配置文件"></a>（2）_config.XXX.yml 主题相关配置文件</h3><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JSON</span><br><span class="line">menu<span class="punctuation">:</span></span><br><span class="line">   首页<span class="punctuation">:</span> / || fas fa-home</span><br><span class="line">   归档<span class="punctuation">:</span> /archives/ || fas fa-archive</span><br><span class="line">   标签<span class="punctuation">:</span> /tags/ || fas fa-tags</span><br><span class="line">   分类<span class="punctuation">:</span> /categories/ || fas fa-folder-open</span><br><span class="line">   #菜单||fas fa-list<span class="punctuation">:</span></span><br><span class="line">     #音乐<span class="punctuation">:</span> /music/ || fas fa-music</span><br><span class="line">     #电影<span class="punctuation">:</span> /movies/ || fas fa-video</span><br><span class="line">   友链<span class="punctuation">:</span> /link/ || fas fa-link</span><br><span class="line">   #关于<span class="punctuation">:</span> /about/ || fas fa-heart</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">＃Favicon（網站圖標）</span><br><span class="line">  favicon<span class="punctuation">:</span> /img/<span class="number">1.</span>png</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">＃Avatar (頭像)</span><br><span class="line">  avatar<span class="punctuation">:</span></span><br><span class="line">    img<span class="punctuation">:</span> /img/<span class="number">1.</span>png</span><br><span class="line">    effect<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span></span><br><span class="line">    ble<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line">#Typewriter Effect (打字效果)</span><br><span class="line">  effect<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line">#loop (循環打字)</span><br><span class="line">  loop<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">true</span></span></span><br><span class="line">#source 調用第三方服務</span><br><span class="line">#source<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span> 關閉調用</span><br><span class="line">#source<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span></span><br><span class="line">#source<span class="punctuation">:</span> https<span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="comment">//hitokoto.cn/</span></span><br><span class="line">#source<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="number">2</span> http<span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="comment">//yijuzhan.com/</span></span><br><span class="line">#source<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="number">3</span>  調用今日詩詞（簡體） https<span class="punctuation">:</span><span class="comment">//www.jinrishici.com/</span></span><br><span class="line">#subtitle 會先顯示 source <span class="punctuation">,</span> 再顯示 sub 的內容</span><br><span class="line">#source<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span></span><br><span class="line">#如果關閉打字效果，subtitle 只會顯示 sub 的第一行文字</span><br><span class="line">sub<span class="punctuation">:</span></span><br><span class="line">   - 没有什么比快乐更重要!</span><br><span class="line">   - 人生不如意<span class="punctuation">,</span>十有八九</span><br><span class="line">   - 笑一笑，长命百岁.</span><br><span class="line">          #Loading Animation (加載動畫)</span><br><span class="line">          preloader<span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="literal"><span class="keyword">false</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
